TEXT.TITLE: CIRCLE FINE ART TO BEGIN TRADING ON NASDAQ
TEXT.BODY: Circle Fine Art Corp said its common stock will be included in the next expansion of the NASDAQ National Market System to take place April 7. Circle Fine Art said its quotation symbol will be <CFNE>. Reuter
